<div data-label="Heading" id="e-1580154936283" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1580154936283"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1><i>written by Mia Montalvo</i></h1></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" id="r-1569330697238" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1569330697238" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1543568570869" data-id="1543568570869" style="min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697217" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697217"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>With the weather warming up and Summer approaching, it can feel tempting to stray from a vegan diet. If you’re looking for some refreshing ideas to take to the beach, outside at the park, or to have at your next barbeque, that isn't just ice cream, you’re in luck.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><i>We’ve rounded up our favorite summer vegan sweet treats that are both cruelty-free and delicious!&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1578321658508" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1578321658508"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>1. Wake Me Up: Tropical Chia Seed Pudding<br></h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1580766535524" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1" data-id="1580766535524"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://createmindfully.com/tropical-chia-pudding/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/da655f4b-82d8-412c-af9b-b9b565eedc4a/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697271" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697271"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.43px;">Refreshing and fruity, this <a href="https://createmindfully.com/tropical-chia-pudding/" class="">Tropical Chia Seed Pudding</a> is a super healthy yet decadent option is our go-to Summer breakfast. Packed with protein, and sweetened by fresh mango, banana, and crispy coconut flakes, this recipe will surely become a Summer staple in your kitchen.</span><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1583868243529" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1583868243529"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>2. Light &amp; Sweet: Vegan Apple Cake with Cinnamon Custard<br></h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1584455612887" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1584455612887"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://www.veganricha.com/vegan-apple-cake-with-cinnamon-custard/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/9e6d4e25-c0cf-4385-816b-740f48ea4870/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1583868265184" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1583868265184"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br><span style="letter-spacing: 0.43px;">This super-light and fluffy&nbsp;<a href="https://www.veganricha.com/vegan-apple-cake-with-cinnamon-custard/" class="">vegan apple cake</a> is made of only six ingredients and is perfect for a midday snack or after dinner treat! Serve with vegan vanilla ice-cream or make the cinnamon vegan custard Vegan Richa recommends.<br></span></p><p>&nbsp;<br></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1580152772200" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1580152772200"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>3. The Perfect Cold-Brew Smoothie Fix</h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1585606499396" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1585606499396"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://minimalistbaker.com/creamy-cold-brew-coffee-smoothie/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/66924c51-b986-435b-862f-208246d1b33f/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697333" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697333"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697294" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697294"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>An easy recipe to make for your Summer mornings, this <a href="https://minimalistbaker.com/creamy-cold-brew-coffee-smoothie/" class="">Cold Brew Coffee Smoothie</a> by Minimalist Baker is made strategically by first freezing coconut milk into ice cubes. Entirely customizable, add more or less caffeine (cold brew) to this smoothie and just a bit of banana for a creamy consistency.&nbsp;<br></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1584453975715" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1584453975715"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>4. Not Your Mom’s Spicy Fruit Salad<br></h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1585605589557" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1585605589557"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://minimalistbaker.com/spicy-fruit-salad/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/eaa383cf-a9b6-4b10-90fb-5c37c569fd4c/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697334" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697334"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1578321958063" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1578321958063"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.43px;"><br></span></p><p>Inspired by a Mexican classic, this <a href="https://minimalistbaker.com/spicy-fruit-salad/" class="">spicy fruit salad</a> is a fun twist on your classic, yet sometimes boring cut up fruit bowl. Chilli powder, lime, a touch of sweet agave, and the optional tequila for that bite, this is best served chilled on hot days.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1575480429283" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1575480429283"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>5.&nbsp; Yes Way, Watermelon Frose <br></h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1585606532254" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1585606532254"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://inquiringchef.com/watermelon-frose/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/64a87e84-d8c2-45d7-a5a3-121c6fd31a57/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697351" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697351"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>Combining our two Summer must haves: Rose &amp; fresh watermelon –– this slushie is a super fun and easy beverage to make for the days you’re craving something sweet and refreshing.&nbsp;<br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" id="e-1591733948696" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1591733948696"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>6.&nbsp; Ending The Night: Homemade Vegan Strawberry Shortcake <br></h1></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1591733950997" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1591733950997"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://simple-veganista.com/vegan-strawberry-shortcake/" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/16bc9afb-450a-49bd-83c0-7b071c360637/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1578322094530" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1578322094530"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1569330697193" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697193"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><div><br></div>This dessert is made for that midnight craving. Sandwiched between two biscuits is fresh sliced strawberries and coconut whipped cream, it’s a healthier option that will still satisfy your sweet tooth.<div><br></div><div><br></div><div><i>We hope you love these recipes from our Summer round up! Be sure to tell us in the comments below which one of these vegan summer treats is your favorite, and share with your friends and family!&nbsp;</i>&nbsp;<br><div><br></div><div><br></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Separator" id="e-1569330697232" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1" data-id="1569330697232"><div class="elm gf-elm-center" data-align="left"><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><!--gfsplit-->
